  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Aurix has the following safety measures to detect errors in SRAM"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Error Detection and Correction Codes / Logic",
        "Address Error Monitor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Any corruption in HW will be notified to SMU. SMU triggers the interrupt which will handled by Aurix.SafetyManager component"
    },
